%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-life-career-education%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EJeff%20Bezos%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E'%20house%2C%20his%20former%20housekeeper%20Mercedes%20Wedaa%20had%20to%20swear%20to%20keep%20absolute%20secrecy%20about%20the%20billionaire%20Amazon%20founder%2C%20according%20to%20a%20copy%20of%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-nondisclosure-agreements-silence-control-workers-silicon-valley-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enondisclosure%20agreement%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20included%20in%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Bezos%20considers%20that%20preserving%20his%20privacy%20is%20critical%20to%20his%20personal%20safety%2C%20well-being%2C%20and%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agreement%20read.%20%26quot%3BI%20understand%20and%20agree%20that%20safeguarding%20the%20privacy%20of%20Mr.%20Bezos%20and%20his%20family%20members%20is%20an%20essential%20obligation%20of%20my%20agreement%20to%20provide%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20run-of-the-mill%20for%20celebrities%20to%20force%20or%20request%20people%20in%20their%20orbit%20to%20sign%20nondisclosure%20agreements.%20Last%20year%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiger-woods-ex-girlfriend-erica-herman-sexual-misconduct-details-lawyer-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETiger%20Woods'%20longtime%20girlfriend%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20headlines%20when%20she%20accused%20the%20golf%20star%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20but%20said%20she%20was%20prohibited%20from%20saying%20more%20by%20an%20NDA%20he%20had%20made%20her%20sign%20when%20they%20started%20dating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20sort%20of%20thing%20is%20common%20with%20celebrities%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20protect%20their%20image%2C%20their%20reputation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Evan%20Starr%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland%20who%20studies%20nondisclosure%20agreements%20and%20reviewed%20Wedaa's%20agreement%20at%20Business%20Insider's%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20rare%2C%20though%2C%20is%20for%20the%20full%20text%20of%20the%20agreement%20to%20enter%20the%20public%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20the%20NDA%20was%20included%20in%20court%20filings%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-housekeeper-sues-racial-bias-abusive-treatment-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehousekeeper%20sued%20Bezos%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%2C%20alleging%20racial%20bias%20and%20unsanitary%20working%20conditions.%20In%20her%20complaint%2C%20she%20said%20that%20Bezos's%20housekeeping%20staff%20had%20to%20climb%20out%20of%20a%20window%20to%20access%20a%20bathroom%20and%20lacked%20a%20space%20where%20they%20could%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%20at%20the%20time%2C%20an%20attorney%20for%20Bezos%20denied%20Wedaa's%20allegations.%20The%20parties%20entered%20arbitration%20last%20year%20and%20the%20case%20was%20dismissed%20in%20October%2C%20with%20a%20judge%20ruling%20that%20each%20party%20should%20cover%20its%20own%20attorney's%20fees.%20Attorneys%20for%20Bezos%20and%20Wedaa%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20Wedaa%20would%20be%20allowed%20to%20say%20per%20the%20NDA%20was%20limited.%20Even%20the%20identities%20of%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Bezos%20and%20his%20family%20members%26quot%3B%20were%20%26quot%3Bto%20be%20treated%20as%20private%20and%20confidential%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agreement%20stipulated%2C%20as%20were%20Wedaa's%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20opinions%26quot%3B%20about%20them.%20The%20agreement%20prohibited%20Wedaa%20from%20sharing%2C%20with%20any%20person%2C%20at%20any%20time%2C%20her%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20observations%2C%20ideas%2C%20experiences%2C%20images%20or%20impressions%20that%20refer%20or%20pertain%20in%20any%20way%20to%20Mr.%20Bezos%20or%20any%20of%20his%20family%20members%2C%20no%20matter%20in%20what%20form%20they%20may%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Wedaa%20ever%20created%20content%20about%20Bezos%2C%20he%20had%20the%20right%20to%20buy%20it%20from%20her%20for%20%2410%2C%20the%20agreement%20said%20%E2%80%94%20removing%20the%20incentive%20for%20her%20to%20try%20selling%20any%20memoirs%20about%20her%20experience%20working%20for%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWedaa's%20NDA%20also%20focused%20more%20on%20the%20possibility%20that%20a%20third%20party%20would%20bribe%20household%20staff%20in%20exchange%20for%20information%20than%20is%20typical%2C%20said%20New%20York%20employment%20attorney%20Vincent%20White%2C%20who%20also%20reviewed%20the%20agreement%20for%20BI.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBezos%20has%20reason%20to%20be%20sensitive%20to%20such%20a%20scenario.%20The%20billionaire%20was%20rocked%20by%20scandal%20in%20early%202019%20after%20the%20National%20Enquirer%20broke%20the%20news%20that%20he%20was%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-text-leak-lauren-sanchez-brother-michael-sanchez-accused-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erelationship%20with%20now-fianc%C3%A9e%20Lauren%20Sanchez%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Bezos%20was%20still%20married%20to%20novelist%20MacKenzie%20Scott.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20agreement%20Bezos%20had%20Wedaa%20sign%20was%20%26quot%3Bactually%20notably%20less%20punitive%20than%20many%20agreements%20I've%20seen%20employed%20by%20even%20mid-level%20reality%20TV%20personalities%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20said.%20Some%20NDAs%2C%20White%20said%2C%20have%20provisions%20that%20exact%20a%20defined%20monetary%20penalty%2C%20sometimes%20in%20the%20six%20figures%2C%20for%20every%20breach%20of%20the%20agreement.%20Wedaa's%20agreement%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20simply%20gives%20Bezos%20the%20right%20to%20ask%20a%20judge%20to%20instruct%20her%20to%20stop%20disclosing%20information%20about%20him%2C%20or%2C%20failing%20that%2C%20to%20recover%20whatever%20bribe%20or%20fee%20she%20received%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20in%20all%2C%20that%20approach%20is%20shockingly%20upstanding%20as%20compared%20with%20many%20NDA%20agreements%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWedaa%20began%20working%20for%20Bezos%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202019%2C%20shortly%20after%20he%20announced%20his%20divorce%20from%20Scott%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-seattle-homes-hunts-point-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epurchased%20a%20%2437.5%20million%20waterfront%20estate%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20exclusive%20Seattle-area%20enclave%20of%20Hunts%20Point.%20Bezos%20also%20purchased%20three%20nearby%20homes%20that%20residents%20said%20were%20for%20his%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20transactions%20also%20speak%20to%20Bezos'%20penchant%20for%20privacy.%20Bezos%20purchased%20the%20homes%20through%20a%20maze%20of%20trusts%20and%20LLCs%20that%20appear%20designed%20to%20obscure%20his%20identity.%20Business%20Insider%20identified%20the%20properties%20by%20linking%20their%20tax%20address%20to%20an%20address%20used%20by%20Blue%20Origin%2C%20Bezos'%20rocket%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWedaa%20was%20paid%20%24250%20for%20signing%20the%20agreement%2C%20a%20transaction%20that%20Starr%20speculated%20could%20have%20been%20intended%20to%20make%20the%20agreement%20more%20enforceable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20dispute%20were%20to%20arise%20over%20the%20NDA%2C%20%26quot%3BBezos'%20side%20can%20argue%20that%20this%20isn't%20coercion%2C%20it%20was%20an%20exchange%2C%20they%20agreed%20to%20these%20conditions%20in%20exchange%20for%20this%20amount%20of%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Starr%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20contained%20a%20carveout%20for%20sexual%20harassment%20or%20assault%2C%20which%20would%20have%20enabled%20Wedaa%20to%20speak%20out%20if%20she%20observed%20or%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20such%20behavior.%20Several%20states%2C%20including%20Washing