Exxon%20and%20Chevron%20have%20announced%20mega-mergers%20this%20year%20to%20buy%20top%20shale%20producers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Permian%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20engine%20of%20growth%20not%20only%20this%20year%2C%20but%20in%20years%20going%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20Hunter%20Kornfeind%2C%20an%20oil%20analyst%20at%20Rapidan%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EShifting%20tides%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20amped%20budgets%20of%20the%20energy%20behemoths%20highlight%20the%20surge%20in%20US%20oil%20production%2C%20they%20are%20also%20a%20sign%20of%20the%20shifting%20landscape%20in%20the%20American%20energy%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowth%20is%20not%20as%20high%20compared%20to%20prior%20cycles%2C%20when%20oil%20companies%20would%20reinvest%20about%20100%25%20of%20the%20cash%20they%20generated%20into%20capital%20expenditures%20to%20drill%20more%20oil%2C%20Kornfeind%20said.%20Now%2C%20the%20amount%20they%20spend%20is%20about%2040%25%20to%2050%25%20of%20the%20money%20they%20make.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20reflects%20a%20change%20in%20the%20priorities%20of%20US%20oil%20companies%20as%20they%20focus%20more%20on%20shareholders%20returns%20through%20buybacks%20and%20dividends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20US%20shale%20production%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Saudi%20Arabia%20targeted%20in%202014%20%E2%80%94%20isn't%20the%20main%20risk%20facing%20OPEC%20over%20the%20longer%20term%2C%20McNally%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOPEC%20is%20more%20concerned%20about%20inadequate%20investment%20in%20supply%20than%20too%20much%20shale%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20OPEC%20does%20not%20share%20the%20IEA's%20peak%20demand%20view%20and%20therefore%20thinks%20shale%20oil%20growth%20is%20less%20of%20a%20threat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-oil-production-outlook-opec-cuts-saudi-arabia-flood-market-2023-12%5C%22%3EBus