ar%20and%20a%20half%3B%20now%20we%20have%20special%20days%20where%20we%20only%20speak%20in%20Spanish.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMaking%20language%20errors%20helps%20me%20embrace%20imperfection%20and%20strengthens%20our%20relationship.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20conversation%20with%20Renzo%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fdating-abroad-europe-love-relationship-lessons-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebilingual%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20were%20on%20Tinder%3B%20I'd%20seen%20that%20he%20was%20a%20language%20lover%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20flex%20my%20linguistic%20muscles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20languages%20do%20you%20know%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20asked%20in%20Spanish.%20So%20far%2C%20so%20good%2C%20I%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20got%20too%20confident%20and%20started%20to%20ask%20about%20quantum%20physics%20before%20realizing%20that%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20say%20%26quot%3Bquantum%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bphysics%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20was%20suddenly%20relevant%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20God%2C%20what%20have%20I%20done.%26quot%3B%20So%2C%20I%20just%20gave%20up%2C%20switched%20to%20English%2C%20and%20hoped%20I'd%20still%20get%20laid%20anyway.%20We've%20been%20together%20for%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20have%20Spanish-only%20days%20now%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20I%20can%20now%20say%20things%20like%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20God%2C%20what%20have%20I%20done%3F%26quot%3B%20with%20aplomb.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20bilingualism%20of%20our%20first%20exchange%20is%20now%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20our%20relationship.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20help%20of%20my%20iTalki%20tutor%2C%20I've%20improved%20my%20Spanish%20to%20the%20point%20where%20I%20can%20have%20regular%20%26quot%3BSpanish%20days%26quot%3B%20with%20Renzo.%20Since%20Renzo%20is%20Peruvian%2C%20and%20Spanish%20is%20his%20first%20language%2C%20it%20makes%20sense%20that%20we%20should%20communicate%20in%20his%20preferred%20tongue%20sometimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20Renzo's%20English%20is%20still%20better%20than%20my%20Spanish%20%E2%80%94%20he%20watched%20%26quot%3BFriends%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20lot%20during%20his%20childhood%20%E2%80%94%20so%20our%20%26quot%3BSpanish%20Days%26quot%3B%20are%20far%20less%20frequent%20than%20our%20English%20Days.%20(We%20don't%20even%20call%20them%20English%20Days%2C%20actually%3B%20they're%20just%20%26quot%3Bdays.%26quot%3B)%20But%20this%20makes%20our%20Spanish%20Days%20all%20the%20more%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20pushing%20me%20further%20along%20on%20my%20Spanish%20language%20journey%2C%20they%20improved%20my%20ability%20to%20communicate%20with%20Renzo's%20loved%20ones%20in%20Lima%20%E2%80%94%20his%20hometown.%20His%20mom%20and%20I%20can%20complain%20about%20more%20than%20the%20weather%20now%3B%20we%20can%20also%20complain%20about%20the%20neighbors.%20Of%20course%2C%20I'm%20not%20fluent%20yet%3B%20for%20instance%2C%20I%20couldn't%20remember%20the%20word%20for%20%26quot%3Bspoons%26quot%3B%20recently%20and%20called%20them%20%26quot%3Bthe%20little%20eating%20things.%26quot%3B%20Nevertheless%2C%20Spanish%20Days%20have%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESpanish%20Days%20are%20a%20lesson%20in%20staying%20humble%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20Spanish%20Days%20are%20more%20than%20just%20linguistic%20workouts%2C%20however.%20They're%20also%20opportunities%20to%20humble%20myself%20and%20add%20a%20new%20dimension%20to%20our%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20becoming%20the%20type%20of%20person%20who%20calls%20spoons%20%26quot%3Blittle%20eating%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20dispense%20of%20my%20ego%20and%20natural%20Type%20A%20personality%2C%20embracing%20my%20mistakes%20as%20commonplace.%20This%20doesn't%20mean%20I%20don't%20get%20frustrated%20from%20time%20to%20time%3B%20I%20especially%20get%20flustered%20when%20I'm%20telling%20a%20story%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20know%20enough%20colloquial%20expressions%20to%20sound%20cool.%20Ult