e%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHarvard's%20president%20has%20apologized%20for%20her%20statements%20at%20a%20congressional%20hearing%20on%20antisemitism.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20a%20Jewish%20Alumni%20group%20said%20her%20comments%20reflected%20%26quot%3BHarvard's%20overall%20pattern%20of%20deflection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20group%20added%20that%20requests%20for%20meetings%20about%20antisemitic%20incidents%20have%20been%20ignored.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Harvard%20Jewish%20alumni%20group%20said%20that%20the%20university's%20president%20Claudine%20Gay's%20responses%20at%20Tuesday's%20congressional%20hearing%20on%20antisemitism%20were%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20university's%20true%20attitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20Rep.%20Elise%20Stefanik%20asked%20Gay%3A%20%26quot%3BAt%20Harvard%2C%20does%20calling%20for%20the%20genocide%20of%20Jews%20violate%20Harvard's%20rules%20of%20bullying%20and%20harassment%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20context%2C%26quot%3B%20Gay%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Gay%20has%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvard-president-claudine-gay-apologizes-antisemitism-jewish-genocide-remarks-congress-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eapologized%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20her%20remarks%2C%20telling%20the%20university's%20student%20paper%20the%20Harvard%20Crimson%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bsorry%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bwords%20matter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20words%20amplify%20distress%20and%20pain%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20you%20could%20feel%20anything%20but%20regret%2C%26quot%3B%20Gay%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Gay%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bcalls%20for%20violence%20against%20our%20Jewish%20community%20%E2%80%94%20threats%20to%20our%20Jewish%20students%20%E2%80%94%20have%20no%20place%20at%20Harvard%2C%20and%20will%20never%20go%20unchallenged.%26quot%3B%3C%