%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20house%2C%20has%20been%20suspended%20from%20his%20party%20-%20Mayawati's%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party.%20%26quot%3BAnti-party%20activity%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20spelt%20out%20as%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20action%20against%20him.%20%26quot%3BYou%20were%20warned%20many%20times%20against%20statements%20or%20actions%20against%20the%20policies%2C%20ideology%20and%20discipline%20of%20the%20party.%20But%2C%20despite%20that%20you%20have%20continuously%20been%20acting%20against%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BSP%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20A%20suspended%20MP%20is%20bound%20by%20the%20party%20whip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MP%20from%20Amroha%20has%20denied%20his%20party's%20charge%20and%20said%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Bnever%20done%20any%20kind%20of%20anti-party%20work%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20diligently%20tried%20to%20strengthen%20the%20BSP%20and%20has%20never%20done%20any%20kind%20of%20anti-party%20work.%20The%20people%20of%20my%20Amroha%20area%20are%20witness%20to%20this.%20I%20have%20definitely%20opposed%20the%20anti-people%20policies%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so.%20If%20doing%20this%20is%20a%20crime%2C%20then%20I%20have%20committed%20a%20crime%20and%20I%20am%20ready%20to%20face%20any%20punishment%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20media%20this%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ali%20also%20thanked%20Mayawati%20for%20giving%20him%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20ticket%20while%20stressing%20that%20the%20party's%20decision%20against%20him%20was%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ali%20met%20many%20big%20Opposition%20leaders%20after%20BJP%20MP%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20used%20communal%20slurs%20against%20him%20in%20Parliament.%20He%20even%20held%20a%20one-man%20protest%20outside%20Parliament%20yesterday%20to%20demand%20justice%20for%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20who%20has%20been%20expelled%20from%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MP%20from%20Amroha%20was%20seen%20with%20a%20placard%20hung%20around%20his%20neck%20which%20said%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20turn%20(the)%20victim%20into%20(the)%20culprit%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDecorum%20in%20Parliament%20died%20in%20September...%20it%20was%20bombed%20when%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20made%20those%20comments.%20And%20now%20they%20are%20saying%20this%3F%20Today%2C%20(Mahatma)%20Gandhi%20and%20Ambedkar%20are%20crying%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20visibly%20upset%20Ali%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20massive%20political%20row%20erupted%20over%20Mr%20Bidhuri's%20remarks%20during%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20in%20September%20this%20year.%20The%20objectionable%20comments%20to%20target%20Mr%20Ali%2C%20who%20was%20accused%20by%20several%20BJP%20leaders%20of%20using%20derogatory%20words%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20provoke%20the%20South%20Delhi%20MP%2C%20led%20to%20a%20show-cause%20notice%20to%20Mr%20Bidhuri%2C%20known%20for%20his%20several%20controversial%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20MP%2C%20on%20Thursday%2C%20expressed%20regret%20for%20his%20objectionable%20remarks%20against%20Mr%20Ali%20in%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Privileges%20Committee%2C%20which%20heard%20both%20leaders%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP%2C%20which%20avoided%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20today%20accused%20Mr%20Ali%2C%20a%20former%20JD(S)%20leader%2C%20of%20going%20against%20the%20party%20line%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20were%20given%20the%20ticket%20on%20Deve%20Gowda's%20insistence%20who%20had%20assured%20that%20you%20will%20always%20follow%20the%20party%20line.%20Only%20after%20this%20assurance%20you%20were%20given%20the%20BSP%20memebership.%20But%20you%20forgot%20the%20assurances%20given%20by%20you%20and%20indulged%20in%20anti-party%20activities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanish%20Ali%2C%20who%20started%20his%20political%20journey%20with%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%2C%20joined%20the%20BSP%20in%202019%20with%20the%20consent%20of%20JD(S)%20chief%20and%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda.%20Six%20days%20later%2C%20his%20name%20was%20announced%20from%20Amroha%20constituency%20for%202019%20general%20elections.%20He%20won%20the%20seat%20by%20defeating%20Kanwar%20Singh%20Tanwar%20of%20the%20BJP%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20nearly%2063%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702126800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fpipvkt1o_danish-ali-1200-_625x300_01_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmp-danish-ali-abused-in-parliament-suspended-by-mayawati-from-party-for-anti-party-activities-4649152%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Danish%20Ali%2C%20who%20recently%20became%20a%20target%20of%20an%20unsavoury%20exchange%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20house%2C%20has%20been%20suspended%20from%20his%20party%20-%20Mayawati's%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmp-danish-ali-abused-in-parliament-suspended-by-mayawati-from-party-for-anti-party-activities-4649152%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmp-danish-ali-abused-in-parliament-suspended-by-mayawati-from-party-for-anti-party-activities-4649152%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmp-danish-ali-abused-in-parliament-suspended-by-mayawati-from-party-for-anti-party-activities-4649152%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20made%20Mary%20Berry's%20'remarkably%20easy'%20lasagna%20recipe%20with%20a%20refreshing%20twist%2C%20and%20it's%20perfect%20for%20a%20cozy%20night%20in%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mary%20berry%20lasagne%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6573216558e7c0c29a2af377%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20hei