2031%20photos%20placed%20on%20a%20leaderboard.%20My%20group%20and%20I%20were%20told%20we'd%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20play%20a%20maximum%20of%20six%20games%2C%20but%20if%20we%20lost%20the%20first%20few%20games%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20be%20eliminated%20like%20on%20the%20shows.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20bracelets%20awarded%20us%20points%20for%20each%20round%20depending%20on%20how%20well%20we%20performed.%20The%20better%20we%20did%2C%20the%20more%20points%20we'd%20accumulate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20player%20with%20the%20most%20points%20at%20the%20end%20of%20six%20games%20would%20be%20crowned%20the%20winner%20and%20could%20enter%20a%20VIP%20lounge%20that%20would%20otherwise%20cost%20extra%20to%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20blew%20the%20first%20competition%2C%20modeled%20after%20the%20bridge%20game%2C%20Glass%20Stepping%20Stones.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kirsten%20Acuna%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20the%20first%20Squid%20Game%3A%20The%20Trials%20challenge.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65727abc7a3c8094d5dadf8a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20thought%20I%20was%20going%20to%20excel%20at%20this%20game.%20I%20botched%20it.%3Cp%3EKirsten%20Acuna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20challenge%20was%20inspired%20by%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsquid-game-games-ranked-least-most-stressful-to-watch-2021-10%232-the-glass-stepping-stones-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egames%20late%20in%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20In%20the%20show%2C%20players%20are%20placed%20high%20above%20the%20ground%20and%20have%20to%20guess%20which%20of%20the%20two%20side-by-side%20glass%20tiles%20is%20sturdy.%20Guess%20wrong%20and%20you'd%20plummet%20to%20your%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20no%20one%20was%20going%20to%20actually%20fall%20here.%20Th