20umbrella%20shape.%20Turns%20out%20that%20was%20a%20mistake.%3Cp%3EKirsten%20Acuna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20between%20games%2C%20we%20stepped%20into%20break%20rooms%20that%20helped%20decide%20our%20gameplay%20for%20the%20next%20challenge.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20room%2C%20we%20were%20quickly%20asked%20to%20step%20inside%20a%20circle%20with%20one%20of%20four%20shapes%3A%20a%20circle%2C%20triangle%2C%20star%2C%20or%20umbrella.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImmediately%2C%20I%20assumed%20we%20were%20about%20to%20play%20the%20dalgona%20game.%20If%20I%20had%20to%20scratch%20a%20shape%20out%20of%20honeycomb-like%20candy%2C%20I%20knew%20I'd%20want%20a%20simple%20shape.%20I%20chose%20the%20circle.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20alone%20in%20my%20reasoning%3B%20nearly%20everyone%20tried%20avoiding%20the%20umbrella%20circle.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThough%20we%20stepped%20into%20a%20dalgona-themed%20room%2C%20it%20turned%20out%20we%20were%20playing%20a%20different%20game.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Dalgona-themed%20room%20at%20a%20Netflix%20Squid%20Game%20event.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6572834b58e7c0c29a2ae2a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20dalgona%20room.%3Cp%3EKirsten%20Acuna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20entered%20a%20playground-themed%20space%20resembling%20the%20dalgona%20room%20from%20the%20shows%2C%20and%20groups%20of%20five%20gathered%20around%20tables%20marked%20with%20our%20shapes.%20We%20were%20instructed%20to%20open%20the%20tin%20cases%20in%20front%20of%20us%2C%20expecting%20to%20find%20dalgona%20candy%20and%20some%20type%20of%20tool%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20was%20shocked%20to%20find%20several%20marbles%20instead.%20We%20were%20tricked!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20four%20minutes%20to%20play.%20One%20at%20a%20time%2C%20each%20player%20tried%20to%20get%20their%20marble%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20shape%20on%20the%20table.%20If%20you%20succeeded%2C%20you%20took%20back%20your%20marble%20and%20any%20marbles%20outside%20of%20the%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20is%20to%20be%20the%20player%20with%20the%20most%20(or%20at%20least%20a%20large%20amount)%20of%20marbles%20by%20the%20game's%20end.%20Run%20out%20of%20marbles%2C%20and%20you're%20out.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20umbrella%20was%20the%20biggest%20shape%2C%20so%20these%20players%20turned%20out%20to%20have%20the%20advantage%2C%20not%20the%20disadvantage.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20redeemed%20myself%20during%20the%20marbles%20game.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kirsten%20Acuna%20holds%20a%20tin%20full%20of%20marbles%20in%20front%20of%20a%20table%20with%20a%20circle%20in%20it%20at%20Netflix's%20Squid%20Game%3A%20The%20Trials%20event%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657281670ec98e92f74d6003%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20turns%20out%20I%20was%20decent%20at%20marbles.%3Cp%3EKirsten%20Acuna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20first%20two%20rounds%2C%20I%20stunk%2C%20rolling%20my%20marble%20too%20hard%20outside%20the%20circle.%20I%20noticed%20one%20guy%20was%20a%20natural%2C%20though%2C%20so%20I%20quickly%20adopted%20his%20strategy%20of%20gently%20dropping%20the%20marble%20onto%20the%20table%20and%20my%20luck%20changed.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20finished%20the%20game%20with%2011%20marbles.%20He%20had%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI'm%20good%20at%20Operation%2C%20but%20a%20life-sized%20version%20of%20the%20board%20game%20was%20much%20harder.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221168%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Operation%20game%20in%20Squid%20Game%3A%20The%20Trials%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6572876d0ec98e92f74d6057%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221542%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20was%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20get%20some%20of%20these%20items%20out%20without%20hitting%20the%20sides.%3Cp%3EKirsten%20Acuna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20life-size%20version%20of%20Operation%20has%20never%20been%20shown%20on%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20worked%20similarly%20to%20the%20iconic%20board%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20group%20worked%20together%20to%20remove%20fake%20organs%20from%20a%20giant%2C%20coffin-shaped%20box%20while%20racing%20against%20the%20clock.%20Hitting%20the%20sides%20resulted%20in%20time%20penalties.%20Specific%20tools%20were%20required%20to%20retrieve%20each%20organ%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20always%20obvious%20which%20one%20and%20someone%20else%20on%20your%20team%20might've%20been%20using%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20prided%20myself%20on%20being%20good%20at%20Operation%2C%20but%20this%20was%20the%20second%20most%20stressful%20game%20I%20played.%20I%20managed%20to%20get%20something%20out%20successfully%2C%20but%20I'm%20pretty%20sure%20I%20contributed%20to%20a%20few%20penalties%2C%20too.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20blindly%20paired%20up%20with%20a%20team%20for%20the%20next%20game.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20room%20shrouded%20in%20sepia%20lighting%20at%20the%20Squid%20Games%3A%20The%20Trials%20event%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20CA.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6572774e7a3c8094d5dadf63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20paired%20up%20with%20TJ%20for%20the%20next%20challenge%20near%20the%20far-right%20wall.%3Cp%3EKirsten%20Acuna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20we%20stepped%20into%20a%20room%20filled%20with%20sepia%20lighting%20that%20drained%20the%20color%20around%20us.%20It%20felt%20like%20we%20were%20in%20a%20black-and-wh