could%20be%20as%20active%20or%20passive%20in%20this%20game%20as%20you%20wanted.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20very%20close%2C%20but%20we%20lost%20right%20before%20we%20could%20sink%20the%20opposing%20team's%20final%20ship.%20It%20was%20a%20bummer%20to%20lose%20because%20everyone%20on%20the%20winning%20team%20received%20400%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20I%20had%20357%20points%20and%20was%20in%2026th%20place%20out%20of%2031.%20My%20Squid%20Game%20career%20was%20not%20going%20as%20great%20as%20I%20hoped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20were%20then%20asked%20if%20we%20wanted%20to%20stop%20playing%20or%20carry%20on.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223672%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20room%20at%20the%20Squid%20Game%3A%20The%20Trials%20event%20where%20players%20had%20to%20stand%20on%20an%20%26quot%3BX%26quot%3B%20or%20an%20%26quot%3BO%26quot%3B%20to%20continue%20the%20game.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657277ba58e7c0c29a2ae1d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20we%20wanted%20to%20continue%20playing%20the%20game%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20stand%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20room%20with%20the%20circle.%3Cp%3EKirsten%20Acuna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20final%20break%20room%2C%20everyone%20was%20given%20the%20option%20to%20quit%20and%20keep%20the%20amount%20of%20points%20they%20acquired%20or%20to%20continue%20playing%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20you%20lost%20the%20next%20game%2C%20you'd%20be%20eliminated.%20The%20people%20with%20the%20top%20three%20scores%20would%20head%20straight%20to%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20way%20I%20was%20going%20to%20stop.%20I%20needed%20to%20get%20some%20more%20points%20on%20the%20board.%20Nobody%20else%20decided%20to%20quit%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20do-or-die%20game%20was%20Red%20Light%2C%20Green%20Light.%20I%20was%20the%20first%20to%20fi