%20been%20assured%20that%20the%20accused%20will%20be%20arrested%20within%2072%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shekhawat%20had%20earlier%20claimed%20that%20her%20husband%20was%20not%20provided%20security%20despite%20his%20letters%20to%20former%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20and%20the%20state%20police%20chief%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%20expressing%20apprehension%20about%20a%20threat%20to%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20FIR%20filed%20after%20Mr%20Gogamedi's%20killing%2C%20Ms%20Shekhawat%20claimed%20that%20the%20Punjab%20Police%20had%20written%20to%20the%20Rajasthan%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20Umesh%20Mishra%20in%20February%20about%20a%20plot%20to%20murder%20her%20husband.%20A%20similar%20input%20also%20came%20from%20the%20Jaipur%20Anti-Terror%20Squad%2C%20she%20said%2C%20alleging%20that%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20and%20Mr%20Mishra%20did%20not%20grant%20security%20cover%20to%20Mr%20Gogamedi%20despite%20the%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mr%20Gogamedi%20had%20a%20history%20sheet%20with%2030%20cases%20against%20him%2C%20which%20may%20have%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20granting%20him%20police%20bodyguards.%20The%20last%20case%20was%20registered%20in%202016%20for%20extortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20men%20shot%20Sukhdev%20Singh%20Gogamedi%20multiple%20times%20from%20point-blank%20range%20at%20his%20Jaipur%20home%20on%20Tuesday.%20While%20one%20of%20them%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20crossfire%2C%20two%20others%20managed%20to%20flee.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702125960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fff0rpnvg_ramveer-gogamedi-murder-accused-arrested-_625x300_09_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffirst-arrest-in-karni-sena-chief-sukhdev-singh-gogamedis-murder-4649233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20police%20have%20made%20the%20first%20arrest%20in%20the%20brutal%20murder%20of%20Rajput%20leader%20and%20Karni%20Sena