Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Evans%2C%20you're%20fat.%20You%20have%20two%20options%3A%20Lose%20weight%20or%20die.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%202012.%20I%20was%20sitting%20in%20my%20doctor's%20office%2C%20in%20my%20360-pound-plus%20body.%20I%20was%20fed%20up%20with%20the%20world%20telling%20me%20all%20the%20ways%20that%20I%20was%20wrong.%20Getting%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-to-handle-holiday-fatphobia-tips-from-maintenance-phase-cohost-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efatphobic%3C%2Fa%3E%20bullshit%20from%20my%20doctor%20was%20the%20last%20straw.%20I%20was%20hurt%2C%20sitting%20there%20with%20my%20arms%20crossed%2C%20with%20a%20tight-lipped%20smile%20plastered%20on%20my%20face.%20While%20I%20furiously%20tapped%20my%20right%20heel%20in%20the%20ground%2C%20something%20else%20was%20brewing%20up%20inside%20me%20too%20%E2%80%94%20defiant%20anger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20wave%20of%20all%20my%20experiences%20of%20fatphobia%20rushed%20over%20me%20at%20once.%20From%20being%20bullied%20to%20being%20forced%20to%20shop%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bhusky%26quot%3B%20section%20while%20I%20was%20growing%20up%20to%20being%20called%20names%20(who%20could%20forget%20being%20called%20%26quot%3Btittie%20boy%26quot%3B%3F)%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20all%20of%20the%20laughing%20and%20pointing%20and%20all%20of%20the%20times%20that%20I%20fought%20back%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20anger%20inspired%20me%20to%20get%20on%20a%20treadmill%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BScrew%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20said%20with%20a%20half-cocked%20smile.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20gonna%20run%20a%20marathon.%26quot%3B%20Those%20seven%20words%20changed%20my%20life.%20Something%20switched%20on%2C%20even%20as%20the%20doctor%20laughed%20at%20me%20and%20said%20that%20was%20the%20stupidest%20thing%20he%20had%20ever%20heard%20in%20all%20his%20years%20of%20practicing%20medicine.%20Eyes%20open%20wide%20and%20head%20cocked%20to%20the%20side%2C%20I%20nodded%20emphatically%20as%20I%20sucked%20my%20teeth%20and%20angrily%20curled%20my%20lip.%20I%20was%20using%20every%20bit%20of%20effort%20to%20prevent%20myself%20from%20lunging%20at%20him%2C%20picking%20him%20up%20by%20his%20shirt%20collar%2C%20and%20tossing%20him%20against%20the%20wall%20like%20a%20balled-up%20piece%20of%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20run%20a%20marathon%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20die.%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsouth-africa-plus-size-influencer-fitness-class-virgin-active-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELose%20weight%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20die.%20Run%20a%20marathon%20and%20die.%20Let's%20just%20say%20I%20left%20that%20appointment%20looking%20for%20an%20option%20C.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20running%20shoes%20and%20climbed%20onto%20a%20treadmill%20that%20same%20day.%20That%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20my%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI've%20been%20harassed%20and%20got%20lost%20during%20races%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%20I've%20run%20over%20eight%20marathons%20and%20more%20than%20a%20hundred%20other%20distances%20in%20my%20300-plus-pound%20body.%20I%20created%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fslowafrunclub.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESlow%20AF%20Run%20Club%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20I've%20coached%20hundreds%20of%20other%20runners%2C%20becoming%20a%20global%20ambassador%20for%20Adidas.%20I%20have%20also%20been%20featured%20on%20the%20cover%20of%20Runner's%20World%20magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20journey%20has%20been%20far%20from%20traditional%2C%20and%20it%20hasn't%20been%20easy.%20I%20ran%20mostly%20alone%20and%20braved%20just%20about%20everything%20out%20there%20on%20the%20open%20road.%20I've%20been%20heckled%20by%20people%20in%20cars%20and%20on%20bikes%2C%20and%20I've%20even%20been%20harassed%20by%20race%20spectators.%20People%20have%20stopped%20me%20countless%20times%20to%20inquire%20how%20much%20weight%20I've%20lost%20(it's%20none%20of%20their%20business%2C%20plus%20this%20isn't%20a%20weight-loss%20journey).%20Friends%20and%20family%20have%20asked%20me%20why%20I%20participate%20in%20%26quot%3Bwhite%20people%20sports.%26quot%3B%20I've%20participated%20in%20races%20where%20I've%20come%20in%20DFL%20(dead%20fucking%20last).%20I've%20run%20races%20in%20which%20I%20got%20lost%20because%20they%20started%20taking%20the%20route%20signs%20down.%20I've%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhat-to-do-when-dont-feel-like-working-out-running-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erun%20races%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20they've%20run%20out%20of%20water%20and%20finisher%20medals%2C%20unprepared%20for%20the%20slower%20runners%20at%20the%20back%20of%20the%20pack.%20I've%20written%20an%20open%20letter%20on%20behalf%20of%20those%20at%20the%20back%20of%20the%20pack%2C%20and%20the%20response%20was%20%26quot%3Blose%20weight%20and%20get%20faster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENot%20all%20runners%20want%20to%20win%20%E2%80%94%20some%20want%20to%20celebrate%20their%20bodies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20began%20my%20now%20more%20than%20ten-years-and-running%20journey%2C%20all%20I%20wanted%20was%20someone%20to%20talk%20to%20who%20had%20experienced%20exactly%20what%20I%20was%20going%20through.%20Someone%20to%20push%20back%20against%20the%20stigma%20and%20the%20doubt%2C%20to%20put%20a%20hand%20on%20my%20shoulder%20and%20tell%20me%20I%20was%20going%20in%20the%20right%20direction.%20Now%2C%20having%20learned%20all%20my%20lessons%20the%20hard%20way%2C%20I'm%20ready%20to%20share%20my%20knowledge%20and%20be%20that%20voice%20for%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20runners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERunners%20who%20aren't%20running%20to%20win%2C%20but%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsigns-healthier-not-losing-weight-dietitian-tips-2023-9%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSimilarly%252C%2520a%2520new%2520exercise%2520routine%2Cregardless%2520of%2520what%2520you%2520weigh.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecelebrate%20their%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Runners%20who%20run%20because%20they%20can.%20Runners%20who%20have%20been%20told%20that%20they%20can't%20because%20they%20look%20a%20certain%20way.%20Runners%20in%20the%20back%20who%20have%20been%20forgotten%20about%20and%20left%20to%20fend%20for%20themselves.%20It's%20been%20a%20long%20time%20coming%20for%20us%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20pack%2C%20but%20change%20is%20coming%20and%20I've%20got%20your%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EResources%20for%20plus-size%20runners%20are%20limited%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20good%20news%20is%20that%20the%20recent%20cultural%20shift%20toward%20wellness%20and%20body%20acceptance%2Fbody%20neutrality%2Fbody%20positivity%20is%20empowering%20more%20people%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20sizes%2C%20and%20motivations%20to%20lace%20up%20their%20sneakers%20and%20give%20running%20a%20try.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bad%20news%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fplus-size-runners-breaking-stereotypes-2019-10%23latoya-shauntay-snell-is-the-accidental-activist-who-started-running-to-get-healthy-and-ended-up-becoming-a-role-model-for-would-be-runners-of-all-sizes-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENontraditional%20runners%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20larger%20bodies%20are%20extremely%20underserved%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20resources%20tailor-made%20for%20us.%20Most%20instructional%20books%20about%20running%20are%20written%20by%20elite%20athletes%20and%20former%20Olympians.%20They%20provide%20advice%20and%20plans%20that%20are%20useless%20for%20the%20fat%2C%20plus-sized%2C%20slow%2C%20or%20whatever-you-wanna-call-yourself%20runners.%20People%20like%20me.%20The%20same%20goes%20for%20runners%20who%20are%20beginners%2C%20disabled%2C%20or%20dealing%20with%20any%20kind%20of%20physical%20issue%20that%20slows%20them%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20face%20it%3A%20An%20elite%20marathoner%20or%20an%20Olympic%20runner%20can't%20and%20won't%20give%20tips%20about%20how%20to%20prevent%20brutal%20thigh%20chafe%20or%20provide%20running%20plans%20for%20those%20of%20us%20who%20run%2018-minute%20mile