rticleshow%2F105864031.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Obscene%20Asia%20Cup%20Gesture%20Aimed%20At%20Kohli%3F%20Gambhir%20Reveals%20Truth%20Behind%20Act%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20batter%20Gautam%20Gambhir%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%202011%20World%20Cup-winning%20team%2C%20has%20explained%20his%20controversial%20gesture%20towards%20a%20section%20of%20the%20crowd%20in%20Asia%20Cup%20match%20in%20September%20this%20year%20and%20said%20that%20he%20reacted%20the%20way%20he%20did%20due%20to%20some%20fans%20saying%20anti-India%20slogans.%20However%2C%20the%20cricketer-turned-politician%20said%20he%20should%20not%20have%20made%20the%20gesture.%20In%20ANI%20Podcast%20with%20Smita%20Prakash%2C%20Gambhir%20answered%20queries%20on%20the%20issue%20and%20said%20everyone%20reacts%20differently%20and%20has%20a%20different%20mindset%20and%20%26quot%3Bif%20someone%20doesn't%20want%20to%20listen%20then%20you%20react%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20match%2C%20Gambhir%20was%20seen%20briefly%20pointing%20his%20middle%20finger%20towards%20fans%20with%20some%20reports%20claiming%20that%20he%20had%20done%20so%20amid%20slogans%20hailing%20Virat%20Kohli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20am%20going%20there%20and%20some%20fans%20point%20out%20and%20say%20'Hindustan%20Murdabad'%20and%20they%20were%20told%20once%20by%20the%20security%20to%20not%20do%20it...in%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20moment%2C%20I%20accept%20I%20made%20a%20wrong%20gesture%20and%20sometimes%20when%20you%20hear%20these%20things%20you%20react.%20Everyone%20reacts%20differently%3B%20everyone%20has%20a%20different%20mindset.%20If%20someone%20doesn't%20want%20to%20listen%20then%20you%20react%20and%20I%20am%20accepting%20that%20I%20shouldn't%20have%20made%20that%20gesture%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20reacted%20to%20some%20media%20reports%20after%20the%20incident%20and%20said%20his%20reacting%20to%20a%20particular%20name%20were%20not%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20journalists%20showed%20only%20the%20reaction....it%20was%20also%20said%20that%20it%20was%20India-Pakistan%20match%20but%20it%20wasn't%2C%20there%20was%20no%20clarification.%20You%20(a%20section%20of%20the%20media)%20showed%20only%20one%20reaction%20but%20you%20didn't%20move%20on%20from%20the%20IPL%20incident%3B%20you%20want%20to%20continue%20it.%20It%20was%20said%20that%20an%20individual%20name%20was%20being%20chanted%20and%20that%20is%20why%20I%20reacted%20that%20way.%20People%20can%20chant%20anyone's%20name%2C%20I%20don't%20care%2C%20as%20I%20said%2C%20I%20don't%20take%20fights%20personally.%20But%20yeah%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20someone%20abusing%20my%20nation%2C%20I%20have%20the%20right%20to%20react%20anyway.%20I%20want%20probably%20in%20a%20more%20sensible%20way%20but%20things%20that%20have%20been%20written%20and%20spoken%20were%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%2C%20who%20is%20a%20BJP%20MP%20from%20East%20Delhi%2C%20is%20a%20cricket%20commentator%20and%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders'%20team%20mentor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20the%20only%20Indian%20to%20score%20a%20century%20in%20five%20successive%20Test%20matches%20between%20March%202009%20to%20April%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20has%20played%2058%20Tests%20for%20India%20and%20scored%204%2C154%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2041.95.%20He%20scored%20nine%20centuries%20and%2022%20fifties%20in%20his%20Test%20career%20in%20104%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20won%20the%20ICC%20Test%20Player%20of%20the%20Year%20Award%20in%202009.%20Between%202008%20and%202009%20in%2013%20Tests%2C%20he%20made%201%2C861%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2077.54%20in%2025%20innings%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%20206.%20He%20scored%20seven%20centuries%20and%20equal%20number%20of%20fifties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20147%20ODI%20matches%2C%20he%20has%20scored%205%2C238%20runs%20at%20an%20ave