20effect.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20December%208%2C%20Ali%20had%20held%20a%20one-man%20protest%20outside%20parliament%20against%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20expulsion.%20He%20hung%20a%20placard%20around%20his%20neck%20on%20which%20it%20was%20written%20%E2%80%9Cdon%E2%80%99t%20turn%20(the)%20victim%20into%20(the)%20culprit%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20put%20this%20(poster)%20because%20the%20committee%20also%20mentioned%20me%20in%20its%20recommendation%E2%80%A6%20because%20I%20want%20to%20bring%20her%20justice.%20She%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20given%20an%20opportunity%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20Ali%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-expelled-lok-sabha-danish-ali-ramesh-bidhuri-honour-died-when-ramesh-bidhuri-danish-ali-on-mahua-moitra-expulsion-4645867%5C%22%3Ehad%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20one%20side%2C%20the%20whole%20world%20saw%20how%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20(a%20BJP%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP)%20acted%E2%80%A6%20was%20there%20no%20sense%20of%20honour%20or%20decorum%20in%20Parliament%20then%3F%20Why%20now%3F%20What%20is%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20a%20furious%20Ali%20had%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20his%20suspension%2C%20Ali%20said%20that%20he%20is%20ready%20to%20face%20consequences%20by%20opposing%20the%20%E2%80%9Canti-people%20policies%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20In%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20X%20(formerly%2C%20Twitter)%2C%20he%20wrote%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%3EI%20will%20always%20be%20grateful%20to%20sister%20Mayawati%3Cem%3E%20ji%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20she%20helped%20me%20become%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20giving%20me%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBSP%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eticket.%20Sister%20also%20made%20me%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20BSP%20parliamentary%20party.%20I%20always%20received%20her%20immense%20love%20and%20support.%20Her%20decision%20today%20is%20unfortunate.%20I%20worked%20hard%20%3Cspan%3Eto%20stren