n%20the%20most%20crass%20language%20possible.%20Ali%20had%20approached%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20for%20action%20against%20Bidhuri%20over%20remarks%20made%20by%20the%20latter%20regarding%20him%2C%20during%20the%20debate%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20the%20Chandrayaan%C2%A03%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20MP%20was%20speaking%20in%20the%20House.%20During%20the%20speech%2C%20he%20said%20some%20people%20wanted%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20to%20die%20like%20a%20dog.%20I%20intervened%20and%20asked%20him%20what%20he%20was%20saying%20and%20that%20no%20one%20said%20that%20about%20the%20honourable%20Prime%20Minister.%20Then%20he%20called%20me%20names%20which%20included%20%E2%80%98terrorist%E2%80%99.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwatji%2C%20what%20is%20taught%20in%20their%20%3Cem%3Eshakhas%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20Is%20this%20what%20they%20learn%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Modiji%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Epathshala%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%E2%80%9D%20Ali%20had%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbsp-suspends-mp-danish-ali-9061328%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702123074000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F09171916%2FEffect-23.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbsp-suspends-danish-ali-day-after-he-protested-against-expulsion-of-tmc-mp-mahua-moitra%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'You%20were%20warned%20many%20times%20against%20statements%20or%20actions%20against%20the%20policies%2C%20ideology%20and%20discipline%20of%20the%20party.%20But%2C%20despite%20that%20you%20have%20continuously%20been%20acting%20against%20the%20party%2C'%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbsp-suspends-danish-ali-day-after-he-protested-against-expulsion-of-tmc