got%20the%20assurances%20given%20by%20you%20and%20indulged%20in%20anti-party%20activities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanish%20Ali%2C%20who%20started%20his%20political%20journey%20with%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%2C%20joined%20the%20BSP%20in%202019%20with%20the%20consent%20of%20JD(S)%20chief%20and%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda.%20Six%20days%20later%2C%20his%20name%20was%20announced%20from%20Amroha%20constituency%20for%202019%20general%20elections.%20He%20won%20the%20seat%20by%20defeating%20Kanwar%20Singh%20Tanwar%20of%20the%20BJP%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20nearly%2063%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702122540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fpipvkt1o_danish-ali-1200-_625x300_01_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmayawatis-party-bsp-expels-mp-danish-ali-abused-in-parliament-for-anti-party-activities-4649152%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mayawati's%20party%20BSP%20expels%20MP%20Danish%20Ali%2C%20abused%20in%20parliament%2C%20for%20%26quot%3Banti-party%20activities%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmayawatis-party-bsp-expels-mp-danish-ali-abused-in-parliament-for-anti-party-activities-4649152%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmayawatis-party-bsp-expels-mp-danish-ali-abused-in-parliament-for-anti-party-activities-4649152%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmayawatis-party-bsp-expels-mp-danish-ali-abused-in-parliament-for-anti-party-activities-4649152%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kyiv%20says%20IOC%20allowing%20Russian%20athletes%20is%20'encouraging'%20war%20in%20Ukraine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702122522000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105863728%2Cimgsize-43880.cms%22%2C%