nd%20assessing%20their%20adaptation%20to%20different%20roles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scientists%20Equip%20Mice%20With%20Virtual%20Reality%20Goggles%20To%20Study%20Their%20Minds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EScientists%20have%20developed%20tiny%20virtual%20reality%20goggles%20for%20mice%20that%20create%20realistic%20worlds.%20This%20technology%20allows%20them%20to%20study%20the%20animals'%20brain%20activity%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20scenarios.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20believe%20that%20this%20technology%20could%20eventually%20lead%20to%20simulations%20that%20are%20indistinguishable%20from%20the%20real%20world.%20This%20would%20be%20a%20major%20breakthrough%20in%20our%20understanding%20of%20the%20brain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2020%20years%2C%20Daniel%20Dombeck%20and%20his%20colleagues%20at%20Northwestern%20University%20have%20been%20using%20rudimentary%20virtual%20reality%20to%20study%20the%20way%20that%20mice's%20brains%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20their%20previous%20methods%20were%20limited%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20machines%20used%20to%20observe%20brain%20patterns%20were%20too%20large%20to%20be%20attached%20to%20freely%20moving%20mice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20goggles%20solve%20this%20problem%20by%20creating%20a%20convincing%20virtual%20world%20that%20the%20mouse%20can%20experience%20while%20it%20is%20moving%20freely.%20This%20allows%20the%20researchers%20to%20study%20brain%20activity%20in%20a%20much%20more%20natural%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublished%20on%20December%208%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cell.com%2Fneuron%2Ffulltext%2FS0896-6273(23)00893-0%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejournal%20Neuron%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20research%20represents%20the%20inaugural%20instance%20in%20which%20scientists%20have%20employed%20a%20virtual%20reality%20(VR)%20system%20to%20replicate%20an%20overhead%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20we%20have%20been%20using%20VR%20systems%20for%20mice%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurekalert.org%2Fnews-releases%2F1010184%5C%22%3Esaid%20Northwestern's%20Daniel%20Dombeck%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20study's%20senior%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20far%2C%20labs%20have%20been%20using%20big%20computers%20or%20projection%20screens%20to%20surround%20an%20animal.%20For%20humans%2C%20this%20is%20like%20watching%20a%20TV%20in%20your%20living%20room.%20You%20still%20see%20your%20couch%20and%20your%20walls.%20There%20are%20cues%20around%20you%20telling%20you%20that%20you%20aren't%20inside%20the%20scene.%20Now%20think%20about%20putting%20on%20VR%20goggles%2C%20like%20the%20Oculus%20Rift%2C%20that%20take%20up%20your%20full%20vision.%20You%20don't%20see%20anything%20but%20the%20projected%20scene%2C%20and%20a%20different%20scene%20is%20projected%20into%20each%20eye%20to%20create%20depth%20information.%20That's%20been%20missing%20for%20mice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702121640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fnhbk9me_vr-goggles-for-mice_625x300_09_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fscientists-equip-mice-with-virtual-reality-goggles-to-study-their-minds-in-detail-4649214%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20breakthrough%20technology%20overcomes%20previous%20limitations%20by%20allowing%20mice%20to%20experience%20a%20convincing%20virtual%20world%20while%20freely%20moving.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fscientists-equip-mice-with-virtual-reality-goggles-to-study-their-minds-in-detail-4649214%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fscientists-equip-mice-with-virtual-reality-goggles-to-study-their-min