arab-cinema-genre-1235831833%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Farab-cinema-genre-1235831833%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nawaz%20Sharif%20Says%20He%20Was%20Ousted%20In%201999%20For%20Opposing%20Kargil%20Plan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20former%20prime%20minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20on%20Saturday%20said%20he%20was%20ousted%20from%20the%20government%20in%201999%20by%20(late)%20Gen%20Pervez%20Musharraf%20for%20opposing%20the%20Kargil%20misadventure%2C%20as%20he%20underlined%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20good%20relations%20with%20India%20and%20other%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-time%20prime%20minister%20questioned%20why%20he%20was%20ousted%20from%20the%20office%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20prematurely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20should%20be%20told%20why%20I%20was%20ousted%20in%201993%20and%201999.%20When%20I%20opposed%20the%20Kargil%20plan%20saying%20it%20should%20not%20happen...%20I%20was%20ousted%20(by%20Gen%20Pervez%20Musharraf).%20And%20later%20what%20I%20said%20proved%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sharif%20said%20here%20while%20talking%20to%20the%20aspirants%20of%20his%20party%20tickets%20for%20upcoming%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20supreme%20leader%20said%20that%20on%20all%20three%20occasions%20being%20the%20premier%20he%20was%20delivering%20but%20he%20was%20sent%20packing%20and%20that%20he%20did%20not%20know%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20know%20why%20I%20was%20ousted%20every%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharif%20also%20talked%20about%20the%20visit%20of%20two%20Indian%20prime%20ministers%20to%20Pakistan%20only%20when%20he%20was%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20delivered%20on%20every%20front.%20During%20my%20tenure%20as%20PM%2C%20two%20Indian%20prime%20ministers%20visited%20Pakistan.%20Modi%20sahab%20and%20Vajpayee%20sahab%20had%20come%20to%20Lahore%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%20said%2C%20stressing%20improved%20relations%20with%20India%20and%20other%20neighbouring%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20have%20to%20improve%20our%20relations%20with%20India%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20and%20Iran.%20We%20need%20to%20make%20more%20stronger%20relations%20with%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sharif%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20regretted%20that%20Pakistan%20lagged%20behind%20its%20neighbours%20in%20economic%20growth%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELashing%20out%20at%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20party's%20jailed%20former%20chairman%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20Mr%20Sharif%20said%20he%20did%20not%20know%20why%20an%20inexperienced%20man%20was%20given%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20economy%20witnessed%20a%20downfall%20during%20Imran%20Khan's%20government%20(2018-2202).%20Then%20the%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20government%20took%20over%20in%20April%202022%20and%20rescued%20the%20country%20from%20default.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sharif%20reiterated%20his%20demand%20for%20accountability%20of%20former%20military%20generals%20and%20judges%20for%20ruining%20the%20country%20by%20ousting%20his%20government%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20brought%20this%20country%20to%20this%20level%20should%20be%20made%20accountable%20as%20patriotic%20people%20can't%20do%20this%20to%20their%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Sharif%20had%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20want%20to%20come%20into%20power%20to%20roam%20around%20in%20luxury%20cars%20but%20we%20want%20accountability%20of%20those%20(who)%20ruined%20this%20country%20and%20made%20false%20cases%20against%20us.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20before%20his%20return%20to%20Pakistan%20after%20four%20years%20of%20self-imposed%20exile%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20Mr%20Sharif%20had%20hinted%20at%20bringing%20former%20army%20chief%20