2023%2F12%2F09144720%2FF_IGer0XMAAJqis.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20unusual%20to%20do%20a%20post-mortem%20after%20a%20massacre%2C%20and%20so%20the%20forensics%20have%20begun%20after%20the%20electoral%20carnage%20of%20December%203.%20The%20hindsight%20morticians%2C%20of%20all%20hues%2C%20have%20started%20their%20analysis%20of%20what%20went%20wrong%20with%20the%20opposition%20carcasses%20littering%20the%20battlefield%20in%20five%20states%3A%20EVMs%2C%20caste%2C%20Hindutva%2C%20%3Cem%3Epanauti%3C%2Fem%3E%20barbs%2C%20tribal%20voters%2C%20in-fighting%2C%20corruption%2C%20electoral%20bonds%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20endless%20list%20which%20shall%20keep%20the%20pundits%20occupied%20till%20it%E2%80%99s%20time%20for%20the%20next%20bloodletting%20in%20May%20next%20year.%20Not%20one%20to%20be%20discouraged%20by%20my%20lack%20of%20expertise%20in%20this%20field%2C%20however%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20add%20my%20two%20bits%20to%20the%20autopsy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20much%20attention%20has%20been%20paid%20so%20far%20to%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20behaviour%20or%20preferences%20of%20the%20first-time%20voter%20(FTV)%20on%20electoral%20outcomes%20since%202019.%20This%20is%20surprising%20given%20their%20increasing%20numbers.%20According%20to%20available%20figures%2C%20there%20were%2080%20million%20(8%20crore)%20FTVs%20in%202019%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-polls-bjp-congress-drives-register-first-time-voters-8557773.html%5C%22%3Eestimates%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%202024%20are%20150%20million%2C%20or%2015%20crore.%20That%20is%20an%20almost%20two-fold%20increase%20between%20the%20two%20elections.%20Even%20if%20we%20discount%20the%202024%20estimates%20by%2025%25%2C%20FTVs%20will%20form%20a%20sizeable%20proportion%20of%20total%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFTVs%20comprise%20between%2010-15%25%20of%20the%20total%20electorate%2C%20perhaps%20more%20than%20most%20castes%20or%20religious%20denominations.%20They%20constitute%20a%20separate%20and%20distinct%20cohort%2C%20with%20their%20own%20problems%2C%20aspirations%2C%20preferences%20and%20mental%20make-up.%20You%20would%20expect%20that%20all%20major%20political%20parties%20would%20be%20aware%20of%20this%20and%20that%20they%20would%20cater%20to%20them%20specifically%20in%20their%20manifestos%2C%20as%20they%20do%20for%20all%20other%20electorally%20significant%20blocs.%20Especially%20as%20available%20data%20shows%20that%20FTVs%20have%20a%20significant%20influence%20and%20impact%20on%20election%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202014%20analysis%20by%20IndiaSpend%20concluded%20that%20this%20youthful%20segment%20had%20catapulted%20the%20BJP%20to%20power%20in%20the%20five%20states%20with%20the%20highest%20proportion%20of%20young%20voters.%20Below%20is%20a%20table%20indicating%20the%20five%20states%20which%20had%20added%20the%20most%20FTVs%20between%202014%20and%202018%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20each%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%20border%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20cellspacing%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20data-sheets-root%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20cellpadding%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ccolgroup%3E%5Cn%3Ccol%20width%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ccol%20width%3D%5C%22180%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ccol%20width%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fcolgroup%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20data-sheets-value%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3B1%26quot%3B%3A2%2C%26quot%3B2%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BState%26quot%3B%7D%5C%22%3EState%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20data-sheets-value%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3B1%26quot%3B%3A2%2C%26quot%3B2%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BFirst%20time%20voters%20added%20(in%20lakhs)%20%26quot%3B%7D%5C%22%3EFirst-time%20voters%20added%20(in%20lakhs)%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20data-sheets-value%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3B1%26quot%3B%3A2%2C%26quot%3B2%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BLok%20Sabha%20seats%26quot%3B%7D%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3ELok%20Sabha%20seats%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20data-sheets-value%3D%5C%22%7B%