's%20announcement%20of%20the%20massive%20project.%20Mr%20Chidambaram's%20tweet%20on%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20semiconductor%20project%20was%20also%20seen%20as%20alluding%20to%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%20has%20said%20he%20is%20working%20on%20policies%20to%20make%20the%20youth%20of%20Assam%20self-reliant.%20The%20Chief%20Minister's%20Atmanirbhar%20Assam%20Abhiyan%20was%20launched%20on%20September%2023%2C%20under%20which%20two%20lakh%20youth%20will%20be%20empowered%20to%20start%20entrepreneur%20ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20beneficiaries%20under%20the%20scheme%20can%20get%20Rs%202%20lakh%20in%20two%20instalments%20as%20a%20combination%20of%20government%20grants%20plus%20interest-free%20government%20loan%20to%20set%20up%20micro-enterprises%20or%20service%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20declared%20he%20wants%20India%20to%20become%20a%20chipmaker%20for%20the%20world%20but%20those%20ambitions%2C%20first%20laid%20out%20in%202021%2C%20have%20suffered%20setbacks.%20India%20does%20not%20as%20yet%20have%20any%20chip%20manufacturing%20plants%2C%20although%20India's%20Vedanta%20and%20Taiwan's%20Foxconn%20are%20both%20looking%20at%20building%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemand%20for%20semiconductors%20in%20India%20and%20globally%20is%20also%20increasing.%20The%20government%20has%20forecast%20the%20domestic%20chip%20market%20will%20be%20worth%20nearly%20Rs%206%20lakh%20crore%20by%202028%20compared%20with%20Rs%201.9%20lakh%20crore%20currently.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702115880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fq0esk8to_karti-chidambaram-himanta_625x300_09_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarti-chidambarams-request-and-himanta-sarmas-promise-on-tatas-rs-40-000-crore-semiconductor-project-4648969%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTata%20Group%20has%20submitted%20an%20application%20to%20set%20up%20a%20semiconductor%20processin