0Ms%20Moitra%20had%20denied%20the%20allegations%2C%20but%20Mr%20Dubey%20requested%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20to%20immediately%20suspend%20her%20for%20allegedly%20taking%20bribes%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dubey's%20complaint%20triggered%20an%20Ethics%20Panel%20hearing%20and%20both%20him%20and%20Mr%20Dehadrai%20were%20summoned.%20Ms%20Moitra%20appeared%20before%20it%20on%20November%202%2C%20but%20it%20ended%20with%20a%20walkout%20by%20her%20and%20the%20Opposition%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ms%20Moitra%20accused%20the%20panel%20of%20engaging%20in%20%26quot%3Bproverbial%20vastraharan%20(stripping)%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20countered%20saying%20that%20her%20lack%20of%20cooperation%20and%20refusal%20to%20answer%20further%20questions%20led%20to%20her%20premature%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20was%20tabled%20on%20Friday%20and%20Ms%20Moitra%20was%20expelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20accused%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20of%20%26quot%3Bbreaking%20every%20rule%26quot%3B%20and%20claimed%20that%20the%20CBI%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20her%20home%20to%20harass%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702115040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fbd5lh61_nishikant-dubey-bjp-ani-twitter_625x300_09_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-mp-nishikant-dubey-who-pursued-case-against-mahua-moitra-says-this-on-her-expulsion-4648890%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20today%20said%20that%20the%20expulsion%20of%20Trinamool's%20Mahua%20Moitra%20from%20the%20parliament%20gave%20him%20pain%20and%20it%20wasn't%20a%20happy%20day%20for%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-mp-nishikant-dubey-who-pursued-case-against-mahua-moitra-says-this-on-her-expulsion-4648890%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fin