ed%20to%20hire%208-10%20students%20are%20now%20taking%201-2%20students%20each%3B%20some%20are%20coming%20to%20campus%20but%20leaving%20without%20recruiting%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20student%20at%20IIT-Kharagpur%20told%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gloomy%20scenario%20is%20attributable%20to%20the%20slowdown%20being%20witnessed%20across%20multiple%20sectors%2C%20including%20tech%2C%20consulting%2C%20and%20other%20services%20sectors.%20Economic%20shifts%2C%20geopolitical%20economic%20worries%2C%20and%20recession%20fears%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20slowdown%20globally.%20The%20current%20slowdown%2C%20which%20is%20being%20witnessed%20specifically%20in%20the%20information%20technology%20(IT)%20sector%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20drag%20on%20for%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20quarters%2C%20Sekhar%20Garisa%2C%20CEO%20of%20job%20portal%20Foundit%20(formerly%20Monster)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fit-hiring-slowdown-to-continue-for-2-3-quarters-global-slowdown-to-blame-123112900556_1.html%5C%22%3Ehad%20told%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tide%20over%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20IT%20sector%2C%20%E2%80%9Cnon-tech%20sectors%20such%20as%20automobile%2C%20retail%2C%20and%20banking%20will%20be%20the%20saviours%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20tech%20talent%20as%20the%20traditional%20haven%20IT%20sector%20reduces%20hiring%20significantly%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20Businessline%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Finfo-tech%2Ftech-talent-finds-new-haven-in-non-tech-sectors-amid-it-hiring-slowdown%2Farticle67462067.ece%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20also%20concerning%20at%20older%20IITs%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Bombay%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20Madras%2C%20Kharagpur%2C%20Roorkee%2C%20Guwahati%20and%20Varanasi%20(BHU).%20Of%20the%20total%2023%20IITs%20in%20the%20coun