0programs%20and%20schemes%20or%20often%20misled%20into%20believing%20that%20popular%20Rajasthan%20government%20schemes%20such%20as%20Chiranjeevi%20were%20central%20government%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20the%20election%20year%20budget%20of%20the%20government%20announced%20unprecedented%20social%20security%20schemes.%20Rajasthan%20became%20the%20only%20state%20to%20give%20subsidies%20on%20LPG%20cylinders%20so%20the%20poor%20had%20to%20pay%20only%20Rs%20500%20for%20them.%20By%20making%20the%20first%20100%20units%20of%20household%20electricity%20bills%20free%2C%20and%20free%20electricity%20up%20to%202%2C000%20units%20to%20the%20farmers%2C%20the%20government%20effectively%20made%20the%20electricity%20bills%20of%20most%20citizens%20zero.%20With%20the%20Chiranjeevi%20scheme%2C%20Rajasthan%20also%20became%20the%20only%20state%20in%20the%20country%20to%20offer%20free%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20health%20insurance%20to%2080%25%20of%20the%20population.%20Then%20there%20was%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20accidental%20death%20insurance%2C%20an%20Annapurna%20food%20packet%2C%20free%20smartphones%20for%20women%2C%20urban%20job%20guarantee%2C%20increased%20MNREGA%20work%20days%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20our%20informal%20advice%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20decided%20to%20have%20the%20people%20register%20for%20these%20schemes%20in%20camps%20from%20April%20onwards.%20These%20were%20called%20Mehangai%20Rahat%20Camps%2C%20and%20people%20were%20given%20%26quot%3Bguarantee%20cards%26quot%3B%20for%20each%20scheme%20they%20chose%20to%20enroll%20in.%20The%20camps%20completely%20changed%20public%20sentiment%20in%20the%20state.%20Non-stop%20campaigns%20by%20the%20government%20thereafter%20kept%20up%20the%20momentum.%20The%20ratings%20in%20our%20daily%20trackers%20soared.%20The%20government%20stuck%20to%20its%20positive%20narrative%20around%20schemes%20and%20social%20security.%20The%20BJP%20was%20on%20a%20back%20foot%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20it%20had%20to%20clarify%20it%20wouldn't%20stop%20the%20very%20schemes%20it%20was%20opposing%20with%20the%20charge%20of%20fiscal%20irresponsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20election%20dates%20were%20announced%2C%20the%20party%20campaign%20was%20slow%20to%20take%20off%2C%20and%20this%20caused%20a%20break%20in%20momentum%2C%20again%20reflected%20in%20our%20daily%20tracker.%20But%20we%20more%20than%20made%20up%20for%20it%20in%20November%2C%20when%20our%20campaigns%20made%20the%20ratings%20reach%20the%20April-May%20levels%20after%20the%20success%20of%20Mehangai%20Rahat%20Camps.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20take%20my%20word%20for%20this%3A%20a%20post-poll%20study%20by%20the%20Lokniti%20program%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies%20says%20as%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELokniti%20researchers%20note%20that%20the%20Congress%20campaign%20was%20more%20effective%20than%20the%20BJP's%20in%20earning%20the%20votes%20of%20those%20who%20decide%20their%20voting%20choice%20at%20the%20last%20minute.%20They%20also%20found%20that%20Congress%20managed%20to%20reach%20more%20voters%20than%20the%20BJP%20through%20phone%2C%20SMS%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20even%20door-to-door%20campaigning.%20It%20also%20found%20that%20the%20party's%20Seven%20Guarantees%20Yatra%20campaign%20reached%2054%25%20of%20voters.%20Our%20'Seven%20Guarantees'%20campaign%20managed%20to%20get%20a%20crore%20registrations%20through%20missed%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20We%20Lost%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20begs%20the%20question%2C%20why%20did%20the%20Congress%20lose%3F%20Three%20reasons%3A%20First%2C%20as%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20was%20the%20tradition%20of%20'%3Cem%3Eroti%20palatna'%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20ensures%20the%20'%3Cem%3Ehawa%3C%2Fem%3E'%20is%20naturally%20against%20even%20a%20popular%20incumbent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20around%2050%20Congress%20MLAs%20faced%20very%20high%20MLA-level%20anti-incumbency.%20Far%20too%20many%20voters%20liked%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20but%20did%20not%20like%20the%20MLAs.%20Again%2C%20this%20has%20been%20reflected%20in%20our%20data%20for%20months.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20party%20was%20unwilling%20to%20change%20too%20many%20sitting%20MLAs%20for%20fear%20of%20rebellion.%20This%20was%20a%20strategic%20choice%2C%20and%20one%20cannot%20presume%20that%20changing%20the%20candidates%20would%20have%20been%20enough%20to%20make%20people%20forgive%20what%20they%20saw%20as%20the%20MLA's%20poor%20performance%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20This%20was%20no%20rule%20for%20all%20MLAs%2C%20but%20it%20was%20true%20for%20enough%20of%20them%20to%20lose%20the%20election.%20This%20is%20why%20the%20Congress%20has%20lost%2019%20seats%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20less%20than%205%2C000%20votes.%20Some%20candidates%20did%20not%20believe%20they%20could%20win%2C%20even%20when%20we%20told%20them%20it%20was%20close%2C%20and%20this%20reflected%20in%20their%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20eaten%20into%20the%20vote%20shares%20of%20independents%20and%20small%20parties%2C%20not%20the%20Congress.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Congress%20vote%20share%20increased%2C%20even%20if%20by%20a%20negligible%200.23%20percentage%20points.%20While%20the%20BJP%20was%20ahead%20of%20the%20Congress%20by%202.16%25%20points%2C%20its%20total%20vote%20share%20increase%20since%202019%20was%203.61%20percentage%20points.%20While%20the%20Congress%20did%20a%20good%20job%20of%20retaining%20its%20voters%2C%20the%20BJP%20managed%20to%20acquire%20some%20new%20voters%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20democracy%2C%20the%20opposition%20plays%20an%20important%20role.%20This%20is%20why%20it%20matters%20that%20the%20party%20that%20loses%20the%20election%20should%20also%20be%20strong.%20The%20Congress'%20narrow%20defeat%20will%20ensure%20it%20remains%20a%20strong%20opposition%2C%20preventing%20Rajasthan%20from%20becoming%20a%20'dominant%20party%20state'%20like%20Gujarat%20or%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Naresh%20Arora%20is%20an%20accomplished%20political%20strategist.%20He%20has%20worked%20for%20the%20Congress%20party%20for%20Haryana%2C%20Assam%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20elections)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702107480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fqbs6qna8_ashok-gehlot_625x300_09_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fi-worked-on-congress-campaign-in-rajasthan-heres-why-we-lost-4648683%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20worked%20as%20a%20campaign%20manager%20for%20the%20Congress%20party%20in%20the%202023%20Rajasthan%20assembly%20elections.%20I%20want%20to%20put%20on%20record%20some%20observations%20about%20the%20fascinating%20politics%20of%20this%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fi-worked-on-congress-campaign-in-rajasthan-heres-why-we-lost-4648683%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fi-worked-on-congress-campaign-in-rajasthan-heres-why-we-lost-4648683%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fi-worked-on-congress-campaign-in-rajasthan-heres-why-we-lost-4648683%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TVS%20Motor%20donates%20Rs%203%20crore%20for%20cyclone%20relief%20work%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702106594000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-12%2F15%2Ffull%2F1639563180-425.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftvs-motor-donates-rs-3-crore-for-cyclone-relief-work-in-tamil-nadu-123120900235_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20money%20will%20be%20used%20to%20provide%20necessary%20flood%20relief%20and%20support%20for%20the