ing%20denied%20treatment%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20has%20termed%20these%20allegations%20baseless.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20wedding%20ritual%20but%20is%20staying%20at%20one%20of%20the%20resorts%20booked%20for%20the%20weeding.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20pictures%20of%20plucking%20teas%20while%20wearing%20local%20dress%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20and%20were%20reported%20upon%20by%20Kolkata%20outlets%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20diversion%20of%20medical%20resources%20for%20the%20VVIP%20wedding%20in%20Kurseong%20has%20triggered%20repercussions%20for%20the%20health%20system%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20compelling%20locals%20to%20seek%20medical%20attention%20in%20distant%20towns%20like%20Siliguri%20and%20Jalpaiguri%2C%20opposition%20has%20alleged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08175956%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-08-at-11.58.55-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22791%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08175956%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-08-at-11.58.55-AM.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08175956%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-08-at-11.58.55-AM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688360%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22593%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20north%20Bengal%20hospital.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20many%20doctors%2C%20nurses%2C%20and%20health%20workers%20have%20been%20moved%20for%20s