nderstand%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20pay%20attention%20to%20filling%20up%20vacancies%20for%20doctors%2C%E2%80%9D%20Halim%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702039812000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08175443%2FUntitled-design-19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnorth-bengal-mamata-banerjee-nephew-wedding%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20medical%20team%20comprising%20over%20100%20individuals%2C%20including%20specialist%20doctors%2C%20nurses%2C%20and%20general%20practitioners%20from%20North%20Bengal%2C%20has%20currently%20been%20deputed%20to%20two%20luxury%20resorts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnorth-bengal-mamata-banerjee-nephew-wedding%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fairytale%20Of%20New%20York%20rings%20out%20as%20mourners%20say%20goodbye%20to%20Shane%20MacGowan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702039500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F70x70%2Fskynews-shane-macgowan-funeral_6386691.jpg%3F20231208153708%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fshane-macgowan-funeral-pogues-songs-including-fairytale-of-new-york-ring-out-as-mourners-say-goodbye-13025582%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20rousing%20rendition%20of%20Shane%20MacGowan's%20best-loved%20hit%20Fairytale%20Of%20New%20York%20rang%20out%20during%20his%20funeral%20in%20Co%20Tipperary%2C%20Ireland%20-%20as%20stars%20including%20Johnny%20Depp%2C%20Bono%20and%20Nick%20Cave%20led%20the%20tributes%20to%20the%20singer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4212%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fshane-macgowan-funeral-pogues-songs-including-fairytale-of-new-york-ring-out-as-mourners-say-goodbye-13025582%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproje